  "body": "\r\n\r\n#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version:  1.7.3\r\nOS & Version: Ubuntu (Docker)\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n\r\nShould sync up using fast sync\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n\r\n```\r\n...\r\nINFO [11-28|23:29:33] Imported new state entries               count=0    elapsed=532.808µs processed=3981896 pending=17    retry=16  duplicate=0 unexpected=768\r\nWARN [11-28|23:31:05] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=6fea8f23eaa1b5f6\r\nWARN [11-28|23:34:02] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=8df0737b5af6fabc\r\nINFO [11-28|23:34:30] Imported new state entries               count=263  elapsed=9.078µs   processed=3982159 pending=3999  retry=0   duplicate=0 unexpected=768\r\nWARN [11-28|23:34:37] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=2f11578ec215105d\r\nWARN [11-28|23:34:43] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=e2f7c77207d76057\r\nWARN [11-28|23:40:46] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=6788d56813b3549e\r\nINFO [11-28|23:41:07] Imported new state entries               count=384  elapsed=8.215µs   processed=3982543 pending=10044 retry=2   duplicate=0 unexpected=768\r\nWARN [11-28|23:41:20] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=f41c361a0a27af8b\r\nWARN [11-28|23:41:38] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=16a47bd198cfe1cf\r\nWARN [11-28|23:44:10] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=2f11578ec215105d\r\nWARN [11-28|23:47:52] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=6fea8f23eaa1b5f6\r\nWARN [11-28|23:47:55] Stalling state sync, dropping peer       peer=aa5ee49c3a44f337\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\nDocker + Amazon EBS (SSD, gp2)\r\n\r\n```\r\ngeth --testnet --ipcdisable --rpc --rpcaddr 0.0.0.0 --rpcport 8545 --datadir ./.ethereum --rpcapi eth,web3,net --verbosity 3 --syncmode fast\r\n```",
